my-claw/tools/workspace/dev_task_ff635b16.md:5:# Task Spec: Tamagotchi Pet System for CypherClaw
my-claw/tools/workspace/dev_task_ff635b16.md:9:A persistent, evolving ASCII/emoji pet system where each CypherClaw agent (Claude, Codex, Gemini, CypherClaw router) has a unique Tamagotchi-style creature. Pets gain XP from agent activity, evolve through 4 visual stages, and display animated states in Telegram via the existing GlyphWeave DSL and AEAFPlayer infrastructure. Pet state persists across daemon restarts via a JSON file.
