my-claw/sdp/research-ai-music-models.md:1:# Research Prompt: AI Models for CypherClaw Musical Intelligence
my-claw/sdp/research-ai-music-models.md:3:CypherClaw is an AI art installation that composes and performs music in real-time through SuperCollider. It needs LLM assistance for musical decision-making: generating musical intentions, critiquing its own output, evaluating melodic fragments, and suggesting harmonic directions.
my-claw/sdp/research-ai-music-models.md:20:Are there models that can analyze audio waveforms directly? We could feed recordings of what CypherClaw played and get critique based on the actual sound, not just note data.
