my-claw/sdp/prd-agent-runtime-substrate.md:53:| RTS-001 | Create `cypherclaw.runtime.session_manager` as the shared execution entrypoint. It owns shell/session lifecycle, queueing, environment assembly, cwd tracking, and per-run session IDs. | MUST | T1 | - One importable runtime module exists<br/>- Session IDs are stable within a run<br/>- cwd is tracked correctly across commands<br/>- Module is used by daemon and helper tools |
